headline: Tennessee ends Wells Fargo probe after bank scraps net-zero target
summary: The state's attorney general, Jonathan Skrmetti, "commend[ed] Wells Fargo’s pro-consumer decision to step away from utopian policymaking." Seventeen other states had joined the probe.
